Add in sudo nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/000-default.conf
in directory add 
<Directory /var/www/html>
    AllowOverride All
</Directory>
In htaccess put 
  sudo nano /var/www/html/.htaccess
and add in file :
  ErrorDocument 404 /404.html
Restart Apache2 sudo systemctl restart apache2
And now the 404.html file is good.
